{"tid":2108311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李國麟：我未必支持余慧明，不過9月如果護協有人參選我就願意助選","createTime":"2020-07-14T12:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T12:29:28.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e5ce83ab4e24fab2825015d3c467a17dccfb819","tid":2108311,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"如今李國麟宣佈不再參選，護協會否改為支持勝出民主派初選的余慧明？現為護協主席的李國麟指「呢個我就唔知」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，若然護協派人參選，而又覺得有需要的話，他願意為護協的參選人助選。被追問護協是否已決定另行派人參選時，他則稱護協未有討論，「因為我自己嘅決定，我同佢哋（護協）講咗，贏咗（初選），就大家開心繼續選；輸咗（初選），我就離開㗎嘞，護協我都唔做㗎嘞。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200714/ZJ2MLBJKZEGGU4VVF3R3INP7V4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200714%2FZJ2MLBJKZEGGU4VVF3R3INP7V4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=15a6645c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200714%2FZJ2MLBJKZEGGU4VVF3R3INP7V4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=7273f895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200714/ZJ2MLBJKZEGGU4VVF3R3INP7V4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"}]}